mitigation_step: Improve quality control during manufacturing.

title: Missed Sales Target
cause: The demand for the product in the target market turned out to be significantly lower than anticipated, which resulted from inadequate market research, overestimating consumer interest, or changing market trends that reduced the appeal of the offering.
mitigation_step: Improve market analysis and adjust pricing strategies.
